column8: notes"\x3b   i=0\x3b   while read -r dir\x3b do     i=$((i+1))\x3b     drv="$(basename "$(dirname "$dir")")"          # ex: D5\x0adriver_id="${drv#D}"     base="$(basename "$dir")"                      # ex: 20151211160213-25km-D5-DROWSY-MOTORWAY\x0alb=""\x3b case "$base" in       *AGGRESSIVE*) lb="aggressive" \x3b\x3b       *DROWSY*)     lb="drowsy" \x3b\x3b       *NORMAL*|*NORMAL1*|*NORMAL2*) lb="normal" \x3b\x3b       *) lb="" \x3b\x3b     esac\x0art=""\x3b case "$base" in       *MOTORWAY*)  rt="motorway" \x3b\x3b       *SECONDARY*) rt="secondary" \x3b\x3b       *) rt="" \x3b\x3b     esac     acc="$dir/RAW_ACCELEROMETERS.txt"\x3b     gps="$dir/RAW_GPS.txt"\x3b     vid="$(ls "$dir"/*.mp4 2>/dev/null | head -n1 || true)"\x0aacc_rel="${acc#*sensors/}"\x3b     gps_rel="${gps#*sensors/}"\x3b     [ -n "$vid" ] && vid_rel="${vid#*sensors/}" || vid_rel=""     printf "%s
